# Performance Optimization

## Component Optimization
- React.memo for expensive renders
- useMemo for calculations
- useCallback for handlers
- Proper key usage
- Virtual lists for long content

## Media Handling
- Lazy loading
- Progressive loading
- Proper formats
- Size optimization
- Cache strategy

## State Management
- Minimize rerenders
- Local state when possible
- Proper context usage
- Batch updates
- Selective subscriptions

## Network
- Request caching
- Prefetching
- Compression
- Connection resilience
- Offline support

## Metrics
- Load time < 2s
- First paint < 1s
- TTI < 3s
- Bundle size monitoring
- Performance budgets 